  "name": "prompsit-d4-document-structure-integrity",
  "description": "D4 - Document-structure integrity. Structurally-rich HTML documents (headings, paragraphs, lists, a table, a link, an image) whose tree must be preserved and round-trip while only the text is translated. Text is real human translation (D1 core, license inherited); structure is templated. EN -> 9 languages. Open layer = dev (full references) + test inputs + contrastive pack; test/hidden references withheld. Version 1.0 uses oracle-validated machine labels (oracle_validated); human review is not required.",
  "version": "1.0",
  "datePublished": "2026-06-22",
  "license": "https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/",
  "url": "https://mozilladatacollective.com/",
  "citeAs": "Prompsit D4 - Document-structure Integrity (v1.0, 2026).",
